title: 10,000 Maniacs - MTV Unplugged FLAC
description:
MTV Unplugged is a 1993 live album by 10,000 Maniacs. The music was recorded for the MTV Unplugged series and it was also the last album by the band featuring Natalie Merchant as vocalist. The song "How You've Grown" didn't make the cut to the album, as well as three other songs which featured singer David Byrne as a guest: "Let the Mystery Be" (released in Europe on a CD single), "Jolene" and "Dallas".
